sequenceDiagram
    participant Sched as Scheduler
    participant Canary as Canary
    participant Target as Target Endpoint
    participant CW as CloudWatch
    participant Alert as Alerting

    Sched->>Canary: Trigger run
    Canary->>Target: HTTP request
    Target-->>Canary: Response
    Canary->>Canary: Validate response
    Canary->>CW: Publish metrics
    Canary->>CW: Store artifacts
    
    alt Failure detected
        CW->>Alert: Trigger alarm
        Alert->>Alert: Send notification
    end
